{"questionId":"20417","questionHtml":"<p>Find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math> and the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt to solve&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp;e.g. by factorising&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>q</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;or vice versa&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"20417","referenceCode":"21M.2.AHL.TZ1.11a","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find the value of p and the value of q.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.13—Rational functions"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}